This implementation:

1. Adds a `getAllUsers()` method to `UserDAO` to fetch all users from the database
2. Enhances the user list UI with:
 - A modern, clean design with proper spacing and borders
 - A search field to filter users by name
 - A toggle button with icon to switch between online and all users
 - A user count indicator
 - Improved user list items with better styling
 - Custom scrollbars for a modern look

3. Improves user status handling:
 - Updates the `User` class to track online status
 - Updates all users' online status when receiving server updates
 - Shows online/offline status with color indicators

4. Adds search functionality:
 - Real-time filtering as you type
 - Placeholder text for better UX
 - Respects the current view mode (online/all users)

The enhanced UI provides a more professional and user-friendly experience, making it easier to find and interact with users. The search functionality is particularly useful for larger user lists, allowing quick access to specific users.

This implementation maintains all the functionality of the previous version while significantly improving the visual design and user experience.
